OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1782740880
OL,3,CUp to 20 teenagers rescued from rough
OL,4,Cseas in Lancashire
OL,6,FUp to 20 teenagers were rescued from
OL,7,Fchoppy seas off the Lancashire coast.
OL,9,FHM Coastguard said the children were
OL,10,Fhelped on Friday evening in Fleetwood
OL,11,Fafter they got into difficulty in
OL,12,Frough seas "a significant distance out
OL,13,Ffrom the sea wall".
OL,15,FOne coastguard entered the water to
OL,16,Fcarry out a "tethered snatch rescue"
OL,17,Fto save two children in what was
OL,18,Fdescribed as "challenging rescue". A
OL,19,Fthrow bag was also used to rescue
OL,20,Fanother teenager.T
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
