FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1782740880
OL,3,CUp to 20 teenagers rescued from rough
OL,4,Cseas in Lancashire
OL,6,FThree of the teenagers were taken to
OL,7,Fhospital after swallowing sea water.
OL,8,FThe others managed to get back to
OL,9,Fshore safely.
OL,11,FA member of the coastguard team said:
OL,12,F"With choppy waves breaking against
OL,13,Fthe sea defences, this was a
OL,14,Fchallenging rescue. It was clear the
OL,15,Fgroup had been caught out by the rough
OL,16,Fsea and strong tidal currents, making
OL,17,Fit far more dangerous than they had
OL,18,Fanticipated.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1782740880
OL,3,CUp to 20 teenagers rescued from rough
OL,4,Cseas in Lancashire
OL,6,F"What really stands out is that we
OL,7,Fwere called to exactly the same
OL,8,Flocation at almost the same time the
OL,9,Fday before, following concerns for
OL,10,Fteenagers in the sea.
OL,12,F"On that occasion, we found them in
OL,13,Fshallow, flat calm water.
OL,15,F"They were behaving sensibly,
OL,16,Funderstood the local conditions and
OL,17,Fknew exactly what they needed to do to
OL,18,Fstay safe. What a difference a day
OL,19,Fmakes.
OL,21,F"The sea can change incredibly quickly.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU}D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1782740880
OL,3,CUp to 20 teenagers rescued from rough
OL,4,Cseas in Lancashire
OL,6,F"Conditions that appear safe one day
OL,7,Fcan become extremely hazardous the
OL,8,Fnext, and it doesn't take much for
OL,9,Fsomeone to get into serious difficulty.
OL,11,F"Only a couple of weeks ago we
OL,12,Fdelivered a water safety presentation
OL,13,Fto all year groups at Fleetwood High
OL,14,FSchool, and we know several other
OL,15,Flocal schools have also received
OL,16,Fsimilar visits from emergency services.
OL,18,F"We sincerely hope those important
OL,19,Fsafety messages are being listened to.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1782740880
OL,3,CUp to 20 teenagers rescued from rough
OL,4,Cseas in Lancashire
OL,6,F"We're pleased that everyone was
OL,7,Fbrought safely ashore, and we hope
OL,8,Fthose involved have gone home with a
OL,9,Fgreater appreciation of just how
OL,10,Funforgiving the sea can be.
OL,12,F"The last time we conducted such a
OL,13,Frescue only a few weeks ago the
OL,14,Foutcome was much less positive with
OL,15,Fone life lost and another severely ill.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1782740880
OL,3,CUp to 20 teenagers rescued from rough
OL,4,Cseas in Lancashire
OL,6,F"If you're planning to enter the sea
OL,7,Fthis summer, please respect the
OL,8,Fconditions, be aware of the tides and
OL,9,Fcurrents, and remember that the sea
OL,10,Fdoesn't always give you a second
OL,11,Fchance."
OL,13,FHMCG Lytham who were also out on
OL,14,Fpatrol assisted in the rescue.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
